ul.li:
@DataProvider does not work for JTables
          that use Java 6 sorting (Issue
          # 448).

@DataProvider does not work with multiple selection
          lists (Issue
          # 466).

@EnabledWhen/@VisibleWhen may not work
          for Swing/SWT bindings (Issue
          # 486).

@BeforeAction does not work for an 
          @Action that is also a @DataProvider
          (Issue
          # 331).

@VisibleWhen/@EnabledWhen do not work
          for read-only properties (Issue
          # 225)
